    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, wash your <strong>shredded</strong> <strong>spring greens </strong>then pat them dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634642650715-x200.jpg",
