            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1634642666342-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> brown rice </strong>in bowls<strong> </strong>with the<strong> honey miso king prawns & chilli veg</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice?<strong> </strong>Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
